channel.title: Need engineer ny metro area
channel.description: Hi! hope everyone is safe! I am high school junior in Westchester, NY looking to partner with an engineer to outfit some fisher price ford 150s. I have connected with a local United Cerebral Palsy center, which has a nursery school, and wants to do this project. The school also has the PT/OT ready to go!
